Armor	DEF	Giá OpenSea	Tác dụng PvP
Energy Shield (NFT)	112	1.8M VND	Block 112 damage + regenerate 2 HP/sec
Plasma Barrier (NFT)	140	3M VND	Block 140 damage + reflect 10% damage
Quantum Armor (NFT)	175	5M VND	Block 175 damage + 10% dodge
Graviton Field (NFT)	210	8M VND	Block 210 damage + slow attacker 20%
Tier 4 - Legendary NFT (+100% stats):
Armor	DEF	Giá OpenSea	Tác dụng PvP
Quantum Barrier (NFT)	300	12M VND	Block 300 damage + 15% dodge + regenerate 5 HP/sec
Void Shield (NFT)	380	20M VND	Block 380 damage + immune to 1 hit/10sec
Singularity Armor (NFT)	480	35M VND	Block 480 damage + reflect 20% damage
Tier 5 - Mythic NFT (Event only):
Armor	DEF	Giá OpenSea	Tác dụng PvP
Dark Matter Shield (NFT)	650	60M+ VND	Block 650 damage + immune to critical hits
Time Distortion Field (NFT)	850	120M+ VND	Block 850 damage + 30% dodge + slow time 50%
Đặc điểm:
•	Epic+ có passive abilities (regeneration, reflect damage, dodge)
•	Legendary+ có active abilities (cooldown 30-60 giây)
